snippet.title: The Last World - Early Game Trailer - Wishlist Now Steam
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist! Steam...

Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1927520/The_Last_World/

The Last World is a sci-fi simulation game with elements of space, adventure, modding and automation in which the player has to create his own empire from the ruins of the old one.

Subscribe!
Discord: https://discord.gg/B5m78ha2nS
VK: https://vk.com/razorgamestudio

Don't forget to leave your impression and put your thumbs up! This will help me a lot!
